Definition: a fungus with a broadly convex cap that is cream color with a tint of blue over the margin
Example: waxy gills are bluish green to blue-grey; a short stalk tapers abruptly at the base
Synonyms: waxycap, genus_Hygrophorus, m, a, fungus, with, broadly, convex, cap, that, is, cream, color, tint, of, blue, over, the, margin, waxy, gills, are, bluish, green, to, blue-grey, short, stalk, tapers, abruptly, at, base
Category: noun.plant
